HEADWORD: Pearlfish
<hw>Pearl"fish`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any fish whose scales yield a pearl-like pigment used in
manufacturing artificial pearls, as the bleak, and whitebait.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

